name: Pete 🔥#CancelRent🔥 Harrison
tweet: I love NYC. It has kicked my ass and broken my heart but it’s the reason I’m who I am and where I am. This is where I want to be. I’m going to fight for it. I’m going to fight alongside all the incredible people I’ve met who fight for it. We need cities to be a home for everyone

name: Pete 🔥#CancelRent🔥 Harrison
tweet: Even if we can afford to stay in NYC is our family going to be safe in the future from climate change?   I went through Superstorm Sandy in Stuytown. The “plan” to protect us doesn’t cut it 🤯  Our leaders today are being irresponsible and selfish for not taking it seriously.

name: Pete 🔥#CancelRent🔥 Harrison
tweet: My partner and I want to start our family and raise them in NYC like my grandfather did. But I don’t know if I can afford to and it really scares me. It’s too hard for too many people to afford to stay with a family. Most of our friends with kids have left or will leave 😔

name: Pete 🔥#CancelRent🔥 Harrison

name: Austin Tyler Rogers
tweet: Oh and now that's it's all over I was #TeamKen the whole way.

name: Austin Tyler Rogers
tweet: Brad Ken and James got to play the greatest week of Jeopardy ever. A private game amongst the best stewarded by the real GOAT.

name: Austin Tyler Rogers
tweet: No one else is there: just 3 contestants, answering things asked personally to them by an entertainment icon. No cameras no audience no nothing.

name: Austin Tyler Rogers
tweet: And the joy JH KJ & BR must've had playing the world's most fun game with the world's best host.

name: Austin Tyler Rogers
tweet: The MOST important part. What a man, doing what he does best: letting others shine yet subtly injecting his wit and personality into the mix.

name: Austin Tyler Rogers
tweet: Then, Alex.

name: Austin Tyler Rogers
tweet: So the average viewer, myself included, saw on display and were privy to the inner workings of some of the most agile, adept, adroit, other "a" word minds we'd have the privilege to come across in our entire lives. And we marveled at it.

name: Austin Tyler Rogers
tweet: But the category to category clues were insanely tough. And that there were only 0-5 incorrect per game meant we really were seeing the GOATS.

name: Austin Tyler Rogers
tweet: Wrong movie. Relentless nerdy knowledge. That's what we crave. And #JeopardyGOAT delivered. The Daily Doubles & Final Jeopardy were only marginally tougher than usual. I got probably 75% of both.

name: Austin Tyler Rogers
tweet: Disclosure: I don't really watch that much Jeopardy unless I'm studying for Jeopardy. This? Must see TV (™️NBC) because it gave all of us - fans, casual viewers, terrestrial antenna owners - what they crave: electrolytes.

name: Austin Tyler Rogers
tweet: One hour. No histrionics. No breaks. Just clue after clue after clue after clue.

name: Austin Tyler Rogers
tweet: This tournament, the ratings, the viral moments, the social media, the traditional media, the past contestants; everyone was in agreement:

name: Austin Tyler Rogers
tweet: Next, the second most important part: the J! Fans...

name: Austin Tyler Rogers
tweet: It's a Brave New J!, and it's all Holzhauer play style, all the time. The originator will remain the best, pending a random Jennings.

name: Austin Tyler Rogers
tweet: BR and KJ, their new nicknames, had to had to play to his strategy. Thus the disproportionate ratio of pushy chippy Daily Doubles.

name: Austin Tyler Rogers
tweet: Now, @James_Holzhauer: if there's another super tournament all-stars millennium quarter century March Madness tournament, and neither Ken nor Brad are in it, he will evicerate the competition.

name: Austin Tyler Rogers
tweet: No amount of prep can help you if that one weirdo thing that you didn't happen upon doesn't come up. Brad has dunno FOUR MILLION REASONS to be ok tonight.

name: Austin Tyler Rogers
tweet: He played the absolute perfect strategy, but the dice didn't roll his way.

name: Austin Tyler Rogers
tweet: Next, @bradrutter: he knew who he was playing, wagered accordingly, and was just unlucky.

name: Austin Tyler Rogers
tweet: This only leads me to believe his pregame prep was psychotically intense.

name: Austin Tyler Rogers
tweet: Having watched and gotten demolished by Ken, I can only guess how hard it was for him to overcome his risk-averse nature to go all in all the time.

name: Austin Tyler Rogers
tweet: First congratulations to @KenJennings! His first tournament win was literally the toughest and he crushed it.
